Three-two-five fifty.

115
00:07:02,500 --> 00:07:05,990
Fifteen sixty-nine.

116
00:07:05,990 --> 00:07:08,810
Ten ninety-nine.

117
00:07:08,810 --> 00:07:12,220
Eight eight eight thirty.

118
00:07:12,220 --> 00:07:15,620
Two four nine nine.

119
00:07:15,620 --> 00:07:16,620
How was that?

120
00:07:16,620 --> 00:07:17,620
Difficult?

121
00:07:17,620 --> 00:07:20,330
If so, don’t worry!

122
